text: Mhd Arjunanta (born 16 June 2004) is an Indonesian actor. He is known for his role in the 2025 Indonesian horror film Penjagal: Iblis Dosa Turunan. == Career == In 2025, Mhd Arjunanta appeared in the horror film Penjagal: Iblis Dosa Turunan, directed by Tommy Dewo. The film features a lineup of rising Indonesian actors, and Mhd Arjunanta gained attention for his performance in the movie. == Filmography == === Film === * Penjagal: Iblis Dosa Turunan (2025) == References == * * * * * Category:Indonesian actors Category:Indonesian film actors Category:Living people Category:2004 births
